author: Liquicity
body:
It's 20% over NAV, so is LEAP, and PSTH is \~15%. With DGNR, literally every dip below $12 has been swallowed up. People had no problem paying massive premiums for LEAP, or anything blessed by Chamath.

So why can't a company with CSuite/Exec experience from Square, NextDoor, Salesforce, PeopleSoft (owned by Oracle now), Cisco, and Ceridian get the same love?

Just my $0.02
